{"tid":265546,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公關災難專頁：輔仁媒體 對不起！「冒犯」了妳","createTime":"2017-05-31T16:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T11:54:55.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04e9557d4cb07e0ab2aa1f1de21237dd824586c6","tid":265546,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=1893437534271329&amp;id=1648246202123798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1893437534271329%26id%3D1648246202123798&d=%2BodAZQ8ljF%2BCdTIfQ6MkI04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=93ca248a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=1893437534271329&amp;id=1648246202123798</a><br />\n<br />\n【輔仁媒體 對不起！「冒犯」了妳】【災難系列】<br />\n《公關災難》的post首次被facebook刪除，因為一篇與《輔仁媒體》有關的文章，「冒犯」了《輔仁媒體》，男公關們深感抱歉...<br />\n<br />\n被刪除的post與一篇批評歐鎧淳專業有關，為免二度「冒犯」，男公關決定刪除部份涉及《輔仁媒體》的內容才再次上載。另外亦附上各大傳媒對《輔仁媒體》博客批評歐鎧淳專業的報道，供大眾參考。<br />\n<br />\n男公關重申立場，《公關災難》專頁有三大運作原則，一不刪文二不Block人三不窮追猛打，不過被冒犯的話，不介意亦不排除透過司法制度處理紛爭，我們擁有包括傳媒、法律方面領域的專業顧問團隊。<br />\n<br />\n另外，男公關們會嘗試向歐鎧淳及廣告製作團體聯絡，了解是否須要提供公關及誹謗等法律意見，畢竟被冒犯的受害者是她們。<br />\n<br />\n#誹謗 #方丈 #腐乳 #已儲落錢打官司 #要玩就認真玩男公關唔慣小朋友告狀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/18740237_1893426910939058_1765612821104359024_n.jpg?oh=99951f72661a50a622797f933bd99abe&amp;oe=599C78DE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F18740237_1893426910939058_1765612821104359024_n.jpg%3Foh%3D99951f72661a50a622797f933bd99abe%26oe%3D599C78DE&h=46daa55a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/18765825_1893427047605711_3178374713022988188_n.jpg?oh=281e1cd2f9fb3b04781f1485199dc5e5&amp;oe=599D90D6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F18765825_1893427047605711_3178374713022988188_n.jpg%3Foh%3D281e1cd2f9fb3b04781f1485199dc5